ch\": \"#/$defs/SelectPitchAction\",\ndocs/chat-to-ui-actions.schema.json:3077:              \"const\": \"regenerate_pitches\",\ndocs/chat-to-ui-actions.schema.json:3078:              \"default\": \"regenerate_pitches\",\ndocs/chat-to-ui-actions.schema.json:3434:              \"const\": \"select_pitch\",\ndocs/chat-to-ui-actions.schema.json:3435:              \"default\": \"select_pitch\",\ndocs/chat-to-ui-actions.schema.json:4330:                \"regenerate_pitches\": \"#/$defs/RegeneratePitchesAction\",\ndocs/chat-to-ui-actions.schema.json:4334:                \"select_pitch\": \"#/$defs/SelectPitchAction\",\ndocs/chat-to-ui-actions.md:36:| `pitches`     | `regenerate_pitches`, `select_pitch`                                             | Covers “give me more options” and “pick this pitch” flows.                                            |\ndocs/chat-to-ui-actions.md:61:- All selection actions such as `select_genre`, `select_tone`, `select_pitch`,\ndocs/story-workflow-tool-registry.md:38:| `generate_pitches` | `pitches` | `background` | `story.generate_pitches` | `regenerate_pitches` | `StageOperationToolResult` | marks `pitches` in progress and refreshes downstream staleness |\ndocs/story-workflow-tool-registry.md:39:| `refine_pitch` | `pitches` | `background` | `story.refine_pitch` | `regenerate_pitches` | `StageOperationToolResult` | marks `pitches` in progress for a targeted pitch revision |\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
